{"tid":1541023,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞士行程比d意見","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T07:00:53.000Z","uid":64676,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bd7f0ece137790c7a13bbc990aa8995b7bac1a30","tid":1541023,"uid":64676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:18:12.000Z","msg":"Day 1 Zurich<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 Zurich -&gt; Luzern<br />\n<br />\nDay 3 Luzern -&gt; Interlaken Ost -&gt; Zermatt<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 Zermatt -&gt; 5湖<br />\n<br />\nDay 5 Zermatt -&gt; Gornergrat -&gt; Rotenboden -&gt; Gornergrat<br />\n<br />\nDay 6 Gornergrat -&gt; Zermatt -&gt; Grindelwald<br />\n<br />\nDay 7 Grindelwald -&gt; First<br />\n<br />\nDay 8 Grindelwald -&gt; Jungfrau<br />\n<br />\nDay 9 Grindelwald -&gt; Lauterbrunnen -&gt; Murren -&gt; Grindelwald<br />\n<br />\nDay 10 Grindelwald -&gt; Bern -&gt; Zurich<br />\n<br />\nDay 11 Zurich -&gt; Schaffhausen -&gt; Zurich<br />\n<br />\nDay 12 Zurich -&gt; HK<br />\n<br />\n係隔離post見到呢個行程好似都幾好 <br />\n去grindelward 個幾日就睇下邊日好天先上少女峰<br />\n有無其他位可以執下/miss左d必去既地方<br />\n同埋兩條友帶2萬蚊HKD cash 去夠唔夠? 唔會話特別慳<br />\n另外我計晒好似用pass 好似抵過半價卡 同埋方便d?"},{"pid":"ef0476aadeba96bcbf7c73f4606cadc39605f8b3","tid":1541023,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:18:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea857dfe088735afea4fb845e06d6c1717e466d4","tid":1541023,"uid":117906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:20:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0832c76e3a6aa5b032e3e0f85c56aa001e53c04b","tid":1541023,"uid":64676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bd7f0ece137790c7a13bbc990aa8995b7bac1a30","tid":1541023,"uid":64676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:18:12.000Z","msg":"Day 1 Zurich<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 Zurich -&gt; Luzern<br />\n<br />\nDay 3 Luzern -&gt; Interlaken Ost -&gt; Zermatt<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 Zermatt -&gt; 5湖<br />\n<br />\nDay 5 Zermatt -&gt; Gornergrat -&gt; Rotenboden -&gt; Gornergrat<br />\n<br />\nDay 6 Gornergrat -&gt; Zermatt -&gt; Grindelwald<br />\n<br />\nDay 7 Grindelwald -&gt; First<br />\n<br />\nDay 8 Grindelwald -&gt; Jungfrau<br />\n<br />\nDay 9 Grindelwald -&gt; Lauterbrunnen -&gt; Murren -&gt; Grindelwald<br />\n<br />\nDay 10 Grindelwald -&gt; Bern -&gt; Zurich<br />\n<br />\nDay 11 Zurich -&gt; Schaffhausen -&gt; Zurich<br />\n<br />\nDay 12 Zurich -&gt; HK<br />\n<br />\n係隔離post見到呢個行程好似都幾好 <br />\n去grindelward 個幾日就睇下邊日好天先上少女峰<br />\n有無其他位可以執下/miss左d必去既地方<br />\n同埋兩條友帶2萬蚊HKD cash 去夠唔夠? 唔會話特別慳<br />\n另外我計晒好似用pass 好似抵過半價卡 同埋方便d?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:28:30.000Z","msg":"自膠 打錯應該係半價卡抵d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"f6deaae73d9cba51b0fb7a875af1b4d6ce7ce504","tid":1541023,"uid":36034,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:29:51.000Z","msg":"啱啱去完番黎<br />\n瑞士根本唔洗帶cash<br />\n買車飛就用sbb，又係link credit card找數<br />\ncoop 又可以用apply pay<br />\n<br />\n最重要嘅係信用卡唔用淨係拎一款，有d餐廳唔收AE，得AE就gg"},{"pid":"e932deef429e4029fff80ff11daaec78108c7fc4","tid":1541023,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:40:03.000Z","msg":"zurich洗唔洗咁耐"},{"pid":"de35dac3a64bad545d4c15565d5d9d72b9e8e